the magic words to use today,

00:42:26.720 --> 00:42:31.120
I had something to do
with Hidden Figures.

00:42:31.120 --> 00:42:33.750
But, you know, I
mean, it's almost more

00:42:33.750 --> 00:42:35.280
than the book and the film.

00:42:35.280 --> 00:42:38.250
