for the both of us, I think,

00:42:42.710 --> 00:42:47.680
is that the only-- I
think this is true,

00:42:47.680 --> 00:42:49.840
that one of the most
important ways

00:42:49.840 --> 00:42:55.950
that you can shift the culture
is to portray women or people

00:42:55.950 --> 00:42:59.830
of color in a way that
is surprising and new,

00:42:59.830 --> 00:43:04.460
and what is engendered from
that is a new way of thinking.

00:43:04.460 --> 00:43:09.090
And that's what we've seen
in terms of Black Girls Code,

00:43:09.090 --> 00:43:11.460
and it goes on and on and on.

00:43:11.460 --> 00:43:15.190
